cast.overview: A bank teller discovers he is actually a background player in an open-world video game, and decides to become the hero of his own story. Now, in a world where there are no limits, he is determined to be the guy who saves his world his way before it's too late.
cast.title: Free Guy

details.biography: Seán William McLoughlin, better known as Jacksepticeye, is an Irish YouTuber, best known for his vlogs and comedic Let's Play series. As of May 2020, his channel has over 12 billion views and over 24 million subscribers, and is ranked the most-subscribed channel in Ireland. McLoughlin has participated in fundraisers that have raised millions for charity.
details.name: Seán McLoughlin
